{"tid":1953623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"野獸自由行 城市驚現美洲獅","createTime":"2020-04-01T09:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T10:36:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"139ddfacc3628b7e371c242bdbf025c6dffc320a","tid":1953623,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200331/I5DX7P6MROI2JG6IVCAP565JZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200331%2FI5DX7P6MROI2JG6IVCAP565JZU%2F&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=82a96d19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200331%2FI5DX7P6MROI2JG6IVCAP565JZU%2F&h=299e15f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200331/I5DX7P6MROI2JG6IVCAP565JZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n野獸自由行 城市驚現美洲獅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200331/large/1585585216_c174.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200331%2Flarge%2F1585585216_c174.gif&h=1a10e36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首都聖地牙哥宵禁中有美洲獅在市中心遊走。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐下，多國民眾被敦促遵守禁足令留在家中，空盪的城市迎來野生動物進場。動物亦難得擺脫人類活動帶來的噪音和各種干擾，迎來生機蓬勃的春天。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高拔陞：醫院爆煲 病人或回家隔離<br />\n<br />\n巴塞野豬通街走<br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞巴塞隆拿有野豬從山上走到市區；日本奈良的梅花鹿走到鐵路站；印度北阿坎德邦首府台拉登有成年雄鹿奔跑；加州奧克蘭有一群群野生火雞在街上昂首闊步；智利首都聖地牙哥甚至有美洲獅在市中心遊走；地中海不同海岸亦有海豚現身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200331/large/1585585217_e996.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200331%2Flarge%2F1585585217_e996.gif&h=b6036cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴塞隆拿封城街道無人，野豬群趁機「自由行」。<br />\n<br />\n法國自然史博物館研究總監朱利亞德指，野生動物已夠膽隨心所欲地在人類的市鎮漫遊，而狐狸就是探索市區的先頭部隊，「牠們迅速改變行為。當一個地方靜下來時，牠們就會進駐。」<br />\n<br />\n平常於公園棲息的動物和雀鳥如麻雀和鴿子，亦會更敢於探索自己的區域以外的地方，「為其他動物釋放空間」。封城下的人類亦較易聽到鳥鳴，專家指這並不代表交通變得稀疏令更多雀鳥出現，只是較少汽車嘈雜聲會讓人較易聽到鳥鳴，「鳥類一聽到車聲就不會歌唱，牠們現在是釋放自我。」<br />\n<br />\n雀鳥亦得以築巢而不被驅趕，各種動植物亦因不再被人類踐踏、採摘而得以生存。不過有專家提醒，限制入侵性品種的工作現時暫停，或會危害瀕危物種。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"39a9615a1329e1872ed08b4dd4d69138379dccb3","tid":1953623,"uid":24615,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"之前有fake news俄佬政府放老虎🐯上街以防止有人出街違反封城令"},{"pid":"7579691951be8714751f73b04c5a1882bfdcd5db","tid":1953623,"uid":68689,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"香港都有好多狗同豬係到行"},{"pid":"7f67588bcccd1629282c94c1aa0cabd5ac8e1df2","tid":1953623,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"I am legend"},{"pid":"e48b030ff67fefab94eb42255c9c314de5ed7f4f","tid":1953623,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"有幾驚現<br />\n未見過大場面"},{"pid":"88c0964871808577e6d8ff222d8a8eb8190b436e","tid":1953623,"uid":14718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"只不過係大隻啲嘅貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6285a107d6e23870a79d2e9598cba70ab9374a3","tid":1953623,"uid":123895,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUoPKBX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUoPKBX.jpg&h=0781e5dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c416147ffb304cdc3cb00d3e6e40f7af17842289","tid":1953623,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a9615a1329e1872ed08b4dd4d69138379dccb3","tid":1953623,"uid":24615,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"之前有fake news俄佬政府放老虎🐯上街以防止有人出街違反封城令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj